Head first and it bounced off. Smith gets up and has a word with the physio. Seems to be fine. That looked brutal. Slower delivery from Unadkat and Coulter-Nile swung across the line towards deep mid-wicket. Stokes ran to his left and Smith ran to his right from long-on.
